intent.user_query: Find the salespersons who haven't made any sales in the last quarter.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT DISTINCT SalesPersonID FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE SalesPersonID IS NOT NULL AND SaleDate < CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3' MONTH AND SalesPersonID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT SalesPersonID FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE SaleDate >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3' MONTH);

arguments.sql: SELECT DISTINCT SalesPersonID FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE SalesPersonID IS NOT NULL AND SaleDate < CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3' MONTH AND SalesPersonID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT SalesPersonID FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE SaleDate >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3' MONTH);

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
